{"tid":1968682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【慘】港豬主動放無薪假，都要被人炒！","createTime":"2020-04-11T23:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T09:14:18.000Z","uid":202464,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cd8446dac0f1b8e1dcfeb8ff7eadd1f4e1018f67","tid":1968682,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T23:07:27.000Z","msg":"Tommy（化名）現屬會展活動餐飲部員工。<br />\n<br />\n佢話灣仔會展自2月起便開始裁員，包括會展內的餐飲員工、廚師、活動部門的高層、保安等等均有被裁，至今已裁走近100人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他指，有被裁走的同事已服務公司20多年。<span style=\"color: red;\">據知有同事希望與公司「共度時艱」，主動提出減薪或放無薪假等方案，惟最後仍慘被解僱。</span><br />\n<br />\nTommy憶述，以往公司管理層在不同活動、周年晚宴，常將「以員工為最大考慮」掛在嘴邊，炮轟公司「假仁假義」，又質疑公司由2月起「分階段」裁員，只為令員工減低恐慌和不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n灣仔會展由政府和貿發局擁有，由香港會議展覽中心（管理）有限公司管理。"},{"pid":"d51da1063823c724d6330b800fbcae4607c5c7cd","tid":1968682,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T23:14:18.000Z","msg":"共渡時艱"},{"pid":"2ed2851a556b7025125d872457ead3d0dcd97f5c","tid":1968682,"uid":52943,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:03:06.000Z","msg":"港豬有種病,叫一廂情願<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39185f478f827ac53b852464d15a0cb2abede76e","tid":1968682,"uid":191815,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:06:10.000Z","msg":"自作多情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c1a742b42036b52993e6377ed7e2a649d27f9e","tid":1968682,"uid":37666,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:24:54.000Z","msg":"所以我就知香港老闆啲性格<br />\n一見公司唔對路就走<br />\n依家公司真係減薪叫人共渡時艱"},{"pid":"8dc2c914f79d6f8e2da9fabf3b28fa4dbd120a12","tid":1968682,"uid":35430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:27:23.000Z","msg":"奴才真係奴才"},{"pid":"96eb1ec7b2f7c864696922b54f952ad8b19f0e1f","tid":1968682,"uid":76382,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:31:24.000Z","msg":"大公司講感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowe